FBIS4-60829 "drsov084_a_94020" FBIS-SOV-94-084 Daily Report 1 May 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Kozyrev, Christopher To Meet in Cairo 4 May Kozyrev, Christopher To Meet in Cairo 4 May LD0105124094 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1147 GMT 1 May 94 LD0105124094 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Report by ITAR-TASS] [Text] Moscow 1 May -- The Russian foreign minister and the American secretary of state intend to meet on May fourth in Cairo, where they are due to arrive as co-sponsors at the signing ceremony of the peace agreement between Israel and the PLO on Jericho and the Gaza Strip. Andrey Kozyrev and Warren Christopher set up their meeting during a telephone conversation on Sunday. The Russian Foreign Ministry press department reported that the conversation was held upon the initiative of the American diplomat.
